%20situation.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%20last%20night%20to%20discuss%20the%20Bangladesh%20situation%20that%20has%20immense%20strategic%20ramifications%20for%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20Centre%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20state%20how%20it%20plans%20to%20navigate%20this%20neighbourhood%20crisis%20and%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20briefed%20MPs%20at%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20today.%20Here's%20why%20the%20Bangladesh%20situation%20is%20a%20tightrope%20for%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20Is%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20escape%20from%20Dhaka%20in%20turmoil%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20landed%20at%20the%20Hindon%20airbase%20in%20Delhi%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20fly%20to%20the%20UK%20today%20to%20seek%20political%20asylum.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20confirmation%20on%20whether%20the%20UK%20has%20offered%20asylum%20to%20her%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20happens%20if%20the%20UK%20does%20not%20give%20her%20a%20green%20signal.%20In%20its%20response%20to%20the%20Bangladesh%20situation%2C%20London%20has%20only%20called%20for%20a%20UN-led%20probe%20but%20has%20not%20touched%20upon%20the%20asylum%20issue.%20The%20question%20then%20is%20will%20Ms%20Hasina%20then%20stay%20in%20India%20or%20seek%20another%20destination.%20India%20now%20faces%20a%20diplomatic%20dilemma%20and%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20overtly%20backing%20the%20ousted%20leader%20because%20that%20may%20complicate%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20new%20dispensation%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Also%20important%20is%20the%20history%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20relationship%20with%20India.%20Long%20before%20she%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20had%20given%20her%20refuge%20after%20her%20whole%20family%2C%20including%20father%20Mujibur%20Rahaman%2C%20was%20assassinated%20during%20the%201975%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh.%20So%20abandoning%20her%20at%20this%20point%20will%20also%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20decision%2C%20considering%20her%20equations%20with%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Friend%20Loses%20Power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20New%20Delhi%20had%20a%20friend%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20her%20uninterrupted%20tenure%20since%202009%20saw%20a%20major%20boost%20in%20New%20Delhi-Dhaka%20ties.%20From%20road%20and%20rail%20connectivity%20to%20border%20management%20to%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20the%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20strengthened%20during%20this%20time.%20When%20protests%20against%20Ms%20Hasina%20gathered%20steam%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20India's%20response%20was%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%20matter%26quot%3B.%20With%20the%2076-year-old%20leader%20now%20ousted%2C%20India%20must%20now%20build%20bridges%20with%20the%20new%20Dhaka%20dispensation.%20Bangladesh%20Army%20chief%20Waker-uz-Zaman%20yesterday%20said%20an%20interim%20government%20will%20be%20formed%20to%20run%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20role%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20and%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%2C%20who%20backed%20the%20protests%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20will%20play%20in%20the%20new%20government.%20Both%20these%20parties%20are%20no%20friends%20of%20India.%20The%20term%20of%20BNP%20chief%20Khaleda%20Zia%20was%20a%20rocky%20phase%20in%20Delhi-Dhaka%20ties.%20Khaleda%20Zia%2C%20set%20to%20be%20freed%20from%20prison%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20ouster%2C%20has%20in%20the%20past%20used%20her%20anti-India%20stance%20as%20an%20election%20plank%20and%20pressed%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20interfering%20in%20Bangladesh's%20internal%20politics.%20The%20Jamaat%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20close%20links%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20India%20would%20be%20closely%20watching%20the%20developments%20in%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFear%20Of%20Refugee%20Influx%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20concern%20for%20India%20amid%20reports%20of%20violence%20against%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20is%20a%20large-scale%20influx%20of%20refugees%20fleeing%20atrocities.%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20share%20a%204%2C096-km%20border%20that%20is%20very%20porous.%20Influx%20of%20Bangladesh%20refugees%20has%20been%20a%20key%20issue%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Northeast%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20yesterday's%20developments%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20has%20issued%20a%20high%20alert%20across%20the%20international%20border.%20Pradyot%20Kishore%20Manikya%20Debbarma%2C%20leader%20of%20Tripura's%20Tipra%20Motha%2C%20has%20said%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20has%20been%20assured%20that%20no%20infiltration%20would%20be%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Disturbed%20Neighbourhood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20challenge%20staring%20India%20in%20the%20face%20is%20the%20geopolitical%20ramifications%20of%20the%20Dhaka%20turmoil.%20With%20Bangladesh%20slipping%20out%20of%20the%20control%20of%20Awami%20League%2C%20India%20is%20watching%20who%20takes%20over.%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20and%20BNP%20may%20be%20more%20aligned%20to%20China%2C%20and%20Beijing%20would%20leave%20no%20opportunity%20to%20fish%20in%20troubled%20waters.%20This%20is%20not%20good%20news%20for%20India's%20strategic%20outlook%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20past%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20unrest%20in%20India's%20neighbourhood%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20Myanmar%20or%20Afghanistan%20and%20now%20Bangladesh.%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20formed%20a%20bloc%20and%20new%20dispensation%20in%20some%20countries%2C%20the%20Maldives%20for%20example%2C%20have%20suggested%20that%20they%20are%20aligned%20more%20to%20this%20bloc%20than%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20In%20Afghanistan%2C%20the%20Taliban's%20return%20scuttled%20India's%20strong%20ties%20with%20the%20earlier%20government.%20Amid%20this%2C%20the%20boost%20in%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Dhaka%20was%20a%20silver%20lining%2C%20but%20that%20changed%20yesterday%20and%20India%20must%20now%20return%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%20to%20navigate%20this%20new%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722922020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-04%2Fpm-narendra-modi-sheikh-hasina-pti_650x400_71491677395.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protest-bangladesh-updates-india-faces-tightrope-walk-after-bangladesh-turmoil-sheikh-hasinas-ouster-6273466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shocking%20turn%20of%20events%20leading%20to%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20ouster%20as%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20put%20India%20in%20an%20extremely%20tricky%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protest-bangladesh-updates-india-faces-tightrope-walk-after-bangladesh-turmoil-sheikh-hasinas-ouster-6273466%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protest-bangladesh-updates-india-faces-tightrope-walk-after-bangladesh-turmoil-sheikh-hasinas-ouster-6273466%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protest-bangladesh-updates-india-faces-tightrope-walk-after-bangladesh-turmoil-sheikh-hasinas-ouster-6273466%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Know%20all%20about%20Bangladesh's%20violent%20past%2C%20coups%20amid%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20ouster%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722921968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1721621193-8972.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A