ami%20party%2C%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArmy%20chief%20General%20Waker-Uz-Zaman%20will%20meet%20student%20protest%20leaders%20as%20the%20country%20awaits%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government.%20Student%20leaders%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20a%20movement%20against%20job%20quotas%20that%20turned%20into%20a%20call%20for%20Ms%20Hasina%20to%20resign%2C%20said%20that%20they%20want%20a%20new%20interim%20government%20with%20Nobel%20Peace%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20as%20its%20chief%20advisor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Army%20chief%20-%20in%20an%20address%20to%20the%20nation%20-%20yesterday%20announced%20that%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20had%20resigned%20and%20the%20Army%20would%20form%20an%20interim%20government.%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20has%20suffered%20a%20lot%2C%20the%20economy%20has%20been%20hit%2C%20many%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20--%20it%20is%20time%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20General%20Waker.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20-%20the%20daughter%20of%20Bangladesh's%20founding%20father%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20-%20was%20given%20a%2045-minute%20ultimatum%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%20who%20started%20her%20fifth%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20left%20state%20capital%20Dhaka%20in%20a%20military%20aircraft%20for%20India%20after%20resigning.%20The%2076-year-old%20is%20accompanied%20by%20her%20younger%20sister%2C%20Sheikh%20Rehana.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20met%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20evening%20after%20landing%20at%20the%20Hindon%20Air%20Force%20base%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad%20-%20around%2030%20km%20from%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSheikh%20Hasina%20is%20expected%20to%20leave%20for%20London%20later%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%2C%20where%20she%20may%20seek%20political%20asylum.%C2%A0However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20confirmation%20on%20whether%20the%20UK%20has%20offered%20asylum%20to%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EForeign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20chaired%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20fall%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government%20and%20the%20Army's%20takeover%20in%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%20amid%20violent%20protests.%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20briefed%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20parties%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20violence-hit%20nation%20and%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWestern%20powers%20called%20for%20calm%20in%20Bangladesh%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20fled.%20The%20United%20States%20called%20on%20all%20sides%20to%20%26quot%3Brefrain%20from%20further%20violence%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20the%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeaceful%2C%20orderly%20and%20democratic%20transition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20had%20sought%20to%20quell%20nationwide%20protests%20against%20her%20government%20since%20early%20July%20but%20she%20fled%20the%20country%20after%20brutal%20unrest%20on%20Sunday%20in%20which%20nearly%20100%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20taking%20the%20death%20count%20since%20the%20anti-government%20demonstrations%20began%20to%20over%20300.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProtests%20began%20in%20June%20after%20student%20groups'%20demands%20for%20the%20scrapping%20of%20a%20controversial%20quota%20system%20in%20government%20jobs%20escalated%20into%20a%20movement%20seeking%20the%20end%20of%20her%20rule.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722921000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvrbfi6a_bangladesh_625x300_06_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbangladesh-protests-sheikh-hasina-resigns-waker-uz-zaman-after-sheikh-hasinas-ouster-interim-government-formation-likely-today-6272786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bangladeshi%20parliament%20is%20set%20to%20be%20dissolved%20today%20-%20a%20day%