ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlgeria's%20Olympic%20Committee%20accused%20the%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20of%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20claims%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20IBA%20alleged%20on%20Monday%20that%20an%20Algerian%20boxer%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20Paris%20women's%20competition%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20male%26quot%3B.%20Imane%20Khelif%2C%20together%20with%20Taiwan's%20Lin%20Yu-ting%2C%20are%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20after%20it%20emerged%20they%20were%20disqualified%20from%20the%20IBA's%202023%20world%20championships%20for%20failing%20gender%20eligibility%20tests%2C%20without%20specifying%20what%20the%20tests%20were.%20The%20boxing%20in%20the%20French%20capital%20is%20run%20by%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20because%20of%20financial%2C%20governance%20and%20ethical%20concerns%20at%20the%20IBA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOC%20cleared%20the%20two%20boxers%20to%20fight%20and%20both%20are%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20and%20therefore%20guaranteed%20a%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20organisations%20have%20been%20in%20open%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20IBA%20press%20conference%20in%20Paris%20was%20designed%20to%20clarify%20what%20tests%20Khelif%20and%20Lin%20underwent%20last%20year%2C%20and%20what%20the%20results%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIBA%20officials%20including%20Kremlin-linked%20Russian%20oligarch%20Umar%20Kremlev%2C%20the%20organisation's%20president%2C%20who%20was%20on%20a%20remote%20video%20call%2C%20gave%20a%20series%20of%20contradictory%20statements%20to%20a%20room%20packed%20full%20of%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20they%20were%20also%20constrained%20by%20medical%20confidentiality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20clear%20was%20when%20Ioannis%20Filippatos%2C%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20IBA's%20medical%20committee%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Babnormalities%26quot%3B%20were%20detected%20in%20blood%20tests%20of%20both%20boxers%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20boxers%20were%20tested%20again%20in%202023%20to%20confirm%20the%20initial%20findings%2C%20IBA%20officials%20said%2C%20and%20after%20that%20they%20were%20disqualified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20medical%20result%2C%20blood%20result%2C%20looks%20--%20and%20the%20laboratory%20says%20--%20that%20this%20boxer%20is%20male%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Filippatos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20that%20we%20have%20two%20blood%20exams%20with%20karyotype%20of%20male.%20This%20is%20the%20answer%20from%20the%20laboratory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20karyotype%20is%20an%20individual's%20complete%20set%20of%20chromosomes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Human%20Genome%20Research%20Institute%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20a%20laboratory-produced%20image%20used%20to%20look%20for%20abnormalities%20in%20chromosome%20number%20or%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Algerian%20Olympic%20and%20Sports%20Committee%20quickly%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BAlgeria%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20IBA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20recognise%20the%20IBA%20as%20a%20legitimate%20institution%2C%20and%20it%20has%20no%20connection%20with%20the%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20champion%2C%20Imane%20Khelif%2C%20remains%20untouched%20and%20undeterred%20by%20the%20baseless%20claims%20of%20the%20IBA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIOC%20president%20Thomas%20Bach%20and%20high-level%20officials%20from%20Algeria%20and%20Taiwan%20have%20strenuously%20defended%20Khelif%20and%20Lin%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20born%20and%20raised%20as%20women%2C%20and%20have%20passports%20saying%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympic%20body%2C%20which%20has%20effectively%20expelled%20the%20IBA%20from%20the%20Olympic%20movement%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20IBA%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Ban%20arbitrary%20decision%26quot%3B%20over%20disqualifying%20the%20duo%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%20and%20Lin%20a