nded%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20went%20into%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Farida%20credits%20the%20matriarchs%20of%20the%20family%20for%20teaching%20her%20about%20cooking%2C%20she%20says%20she%20also%20learnt%20another%20important%20lesson%20from%20them.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20do%20anything%20half-heartedly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20what%20time%20it%20is%2C%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20making%20an%20order%20and%20I%20realise%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20short%20of%20even%20one%20ingredient%2C%20I%20will%20run%20to%20the%20store%20and%20get%20it.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20deem%20a%20dish%20finished%20until%20I%20am%20satisfied%20that%20its%20taste%20matches%20the%20original%20version%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20order%20your%20feast%20at%208879132817%20or%207506192017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722918585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farida%20Nanavaty%20and%20her%20daughter%20Karishma%20started%20Mumbai's%20Karrylicious%20Kitchen%2C%20which%20delivers%20traditional%20Parsi%20food%20across%20the%20city.%20They%20use%20their%20family's%20150-year-old%20recipes%2C%20passed%20down%20for%20generations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asia's%20second-richest%20man%20finally%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20hand%20over%20his%20company%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20a%20while%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Adani%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b1a341b4912df3ae1914ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGautam%20Adani%20announced%20that%20his%20sons%20and%20nephews%20will%20take%20over%20the%20family%20conglomerate%20following%20his%20retirement%20at%20age%2070.%3Cp%3ESam%20Panthaky%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGautam%20Adani%20plans%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20company%20to%20his%20sons%20and%20nephews%20by%20the%20early%202030s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20is%20a%20major%20player%20in%20multiple%20sectors%20in%20India%2C%20including%20infrastructure%20and%20energy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAdani%20faced%20controversy%20for%20fraud%20and%20bribery%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Asia's%20richest%20men%20said%20the%20next%20generation%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20over%20his%20sprawling%20company%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20won't%20happen%20for%20at%20least%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGautam%20Adani%2C%2062%20years%20old%2C%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20retire%20at%2070%20from%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2024-adani-succession%2F%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201988%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20substantial%20interests%20in%20energy%2C%20logistics%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20and%20aims%20to%20make%20India%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20player%20in%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20and%20self-reliant%20in%20defence%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2FAbout-us%2FOne-Vision-One-Team%2FGautam-Adani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofile%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20the%20group's%20main%20company%2C%20reported%20revenue%20of%20%2411.6%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20and%20Adani%20himself%20owns%20a%2075%25%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdani's%20retirement%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20his%20sons%20and%20nephews%20to%20take%20over%20the%20sprawling%20family%20conglomerate%20by%20the%20early%202030s.%20The%20transition%20will%20occur%20gradually%2C%20and%20Adani's%20successors%20will%20run%20the%20company%20collectively%2C%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Asian%20family%20business%20leaders%20are%20not%20keen%20on%20retirement%2C%20leading%20to%20what%20family%20business%20professor%20Marleen%20Dieleman%20called%20%26quot%3BKing%20Charles%20syndrome%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20next%20generation%20takes%20over%20past%20its%20prime.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGautam%20Adani%20stepping%20aside%20early%20is%20a%20positive%20sign%2C%20said%20Dieleman%2C%20who%20works%20at%20IMD%20Business%20School%20in%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20good%20to%20see%20this%20level%20of%20planning%20and%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dieleman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaran%20Adani%2C%20Gautam's%20elder%20son%2C%20will%20oversee%20cement%2C%20ports%2C%20and%20logistics%2C%20while%20Jeet%20Adani%2C%20the%20younger%20son%2C%20will%20handle%20airports%2C%20digital%20ventures%2C%20and%20defense.%20Nephews%20Pranav%20and%20Sagar%20will%20manage%20consumer%20businesses%2C%20communications%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20finance.%20Adani%20has%20not%20yet%20announced%20a%20successor%20for%20chairman%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Adani's%20public%20announcement%20of%20the%20transition%20sets%20a%20positive%20precedent%20for%20other%20family-run%20companies%2C%20the%20move%20would%20ideally%20come%20with%20safeguards%20against%20conflicts%20that%20might%20arise%20from%20having%20four%20leaders%20steering%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can%20be%20done%20by%20agreeing%20on%20the%20larger%20aspirational%20aspects%20of%20the%20family%20legacy%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20question%20of%20who%20gets%20what%20and%20what%20is%20fair%2C%26quot%3B%20Dieleman%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlacing%20non-family%20experts%20in%20key%20positions%20is%20also%20crucial%20in%20bolstering%20the%20transition%20process.%20A%20company%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20requires%20several%20stages%20of%20leadership%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20comes%20from%20a%20mix%20of%20non-family%20and%20family%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dieleman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leadership%20transition%20comes%20amid%20significant%20controversies%20for%20the%20company.%20In%20January%202023%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhindenburg-research-adani-group-explained-stock-crash-short-seller-profits-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20an%20activist%20short-seller%20investment%20firm%2C%20of%20financial%20misconduct%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20substantial%20decline%20in%20the%20company's%20market%20value.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20company%20was%20also%20investigated%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20for%20potential%20bribery%20involving%20Adani%20entities%2C%20which%20the%20company%20had%20denied%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-18%2Fadani-says-report-on-bribery-probe-by-us-prosecutors-is-false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20March.%20No%20charges%20have%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdani's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-gautam-adani-indian-industrialist-billionaire-wealth-elon-musk-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewealth%3C%2Fa%3E%20surged%20in%202022%20and%20made%20him%20the%20third%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20start%20of%202023.%20However%2C%20following%20the%20allegations%20from%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20his%20fortune%20declined%20by%20more%20than%20a%20quarter.%20Adani%20currently%20sits%20at%20the%2012th%20spot%20for%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%2C%20be