.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20space%20push%20has%20seen%20at%20least%20three%20companies%20announce%2010%2C000-satellite%20constellations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Chinese%20state-backed%20company%20has%20launched%20its%20first%2018%20satellites%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20build%20a%20vast%20orbital%20network%20aimed%20at%20rivaling%20Starlink%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20on%20Monday%20by%20Shanghai%20Spacecom%20Satellite%20Technology%20involved%2018%20satellites%20and%20one%20rocket%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fjjxw%2F2024-08-05%2Fdoc-inchqtkf7752197.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20China%20Securities%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20state%20news%20agency%20Xinhua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20rocket%20lifted%20off%20from%20the%20Taiyuan%20satellite%20and%20missile%20launch%20center%20in%20Shanxi%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20satellites%20mark%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20company's%20effort%20to%20create%20a%2015%2C000-strong%20network%20of%20Low%20Earth%20Orbit%20satellites%2C%20which%20the%20firm%20has%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BThousand%20Sails%20Constellation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20reach%20that%20final%20tally%20by%202030%2C%20per%20The%20China%20Securities%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomestic%20media%20has%20widely%20called%20the%20project%20the%20Chinese%20version%20of%20Starlink%2C%20which%20runs%20about%206%2C000%20satellites.%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20said%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-starlink-satellites-internet%23%3A~%3Atext%3DToday%252C%2520the%2520company%2520has%2520over%2Cto%252042%252C000%2520satellites%2520into%2520space.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeventually%20host%20a%20network%20of%2042%2C000%20satellites.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Thousand%20Sails%20Constellation%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20G60%20project%2C%20is%20one%20of%20three%20planned%20major%20satellite%20networks%20in%20the%20country.%20Each%20is%20expected%20to%20field%2010%2C000%20or%20more%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20are%20anticipated%20to%20orbit%20between%20200%20and%201%2C200%20miles%20above%20the%20Earth's%20surface%2C%20which%20is%20also%20where%20Starlink%20satellites%20are%20generally%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20constellations%2C%20along%20with%20dozens%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-elon-musk-starlink-low-orbit-satellites-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eambitious%20space%20projects%20from%20other%20Chinese%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20fueled%20by%20a%20recent%20push%20from%20the%20central%20government%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F09%2F22%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-private-sector-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloop%20the%20private%20sector%20into%20its%20science%20and%20technology%20goals.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20hopes%20to%20create%20its%20own%20versions%20of%20vital%20technologies%20and%20infrastructure%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20its%20industries%20self-reliant%20and%20hedged%20against%20possible%20foreign%20influence%20or%20pressures%20%E2%80%94%20or%20if%20needed%2C%20war%20with%20the%20United%20States%20or%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShanghai%20Spacecom%20Satellite%20Technology%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20Shanghai%20municipal%20government%2C%20but%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20it's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fspace%2Fshanghai-backed-firm-raises-933-mln-build-satellite-constellation-2024-02-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20funds%20from%20private%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20state-owned%20enterprises%20for%20its%20Thousand%20Sails%20Constellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20other%20constellations%20are%20expected%20to%20bring%20another%2