ttler%20to%20reach%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%20men's%20singles%20event%2C%20the%20rest%20exited%20the%20tournament%20in%20an%20underwhelming%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.%20Sindhu%20lost%20to%20China's%20He%20Bing%20Jiao%20in%20the%20Round%20of%2016%20in%20the%20women's%20singles%2C%20Satwiksairaj%20Rankireddy%20and%20Chirag%20Shetty%20lost%20to%20Malaysia's%20Aaron%20Chia%20and%20Soh%20Wooi%20Yik%20in%20the%20men's%20doubles%20quarterfinals.%20H.S.%20Prannoy%20was%20eliminated%20by%20Lakshya%20Sen%20in%20the%20Round%20of%2016%20whereas%20Ashwini%20Ponnappa%20and%20Tanisha%20Crasto%20did%20not%20even%20make%20it%20out%20of%20the%20Group%20Stage%20in%20the%20women's%20doubles%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20little%20disappointed%20in%20our%20performance%20that%20we%20could%20not%20even%20get%20a%20single%20medal%20from%20Badminton.%20Like%20I%20have%20said%20before%2C%20we%20were%20contenders%20for%20three%20medals%20so%20at%20least%20one%20would%20have%20made%20me%20happy.%20But%20having%20said%20this%2C%20this%20time%20the%20Government%2C%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20and%20Sports%20Ministry%20everybody%20has%20done%20their%20best%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20could%20have%20done%20anything%20more%20than%20what%20the%20Government%20has%20done%20so%20I%20think%20the%20players%20also%20need%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E100%25%20straight-talk%20from%20Prakash%20Padukone.%20Must%20watch.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn3ZdqpWkyZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fn3ZdqpWkyZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shiv%20Aroor%20(%40ShivAroor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShivAroor%2Fstatus%2F1820516718890111340%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3