lds%20'Around-The-Clock'%20Crisis%20Talks%20To%20Avoid%20Israel-Iran%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20held%20crisis%20talks%20on%20Monday%20on%20a%20potential%20Iranian%20counterattack%20on%20Israel%20as%20his%20administration%20said%20it%20was%20working%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20avoid%20all-out%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBiden%20and%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20engaged%20in%20frantic%20diplomacy%20to%20try%20to%20ease%20tensions%20sparked%20by%20a%20suspected%20Israeli%20attack%20that%20killed%20Hamas%20political%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20called%20King%20Abdullah%20II%20of%20Jordan%2C%20which%20helped%20down%20Iranian%20drones%20and%20missiles%20in%20an%20earlier%20showdown%20in%20April%2C%20while%20Blinken%20called%20top%20officials%20in%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%2C%20the%20key%20intermediaries%20seeking%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20the%2010-month%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20engaged%20in%20intense%20diplomacy%2C%20pretty%20much%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20with%20a%20very%20simple%20message%20--%20all%20parties%20must%20refrain%20from%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said%20after%20joining%20other%20top%20officials%20in%20a%20White%20House%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20critical%20that%20we%20break%20this%20cycle%20by%20reaching%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blinken%2C%20who%20has%20also%20spoken%20since%20Sunday%20with%20G7%20counterparts%20and%20Iraq's%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20multiple%20US%20personnel%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20rocket%20attack%20on%20a%20base%20in%20Iraq%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20already%20heightened%20regional%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20had%20been%20hoping%20in%20his%20final%20months%20in%20office%20to%20end%20the%20Gaza%20war%20and%20work%20on%20clinching%20a%20landmark%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20has%20boosted%20the%20US%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20to%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20staunchly%20backing%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20Biden%20has%20made%20clear%20his%20frustration%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20ceasefire%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinken%2C%20who%20has%20warned%20that%20Iran%20could%20strike%20soon%2C%20made%20a%20new%20pitch%20for%20Biden's%20ceasefire%20plan%20that%20would%20freeze%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%20and%20return%20hostages%20seized%20in%20the%20October%207%20mega-attack%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ceasefire%20%26quot%3Bwill%20unlock%20possibilities%20for%20more%20enduring%20calm%2C%20not%20only%20in%20Gaza%20itself%2C%20but%20in%20other%20areas%20where%20the%20conflict%20could%20spread%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said%20as%20he%20met%20Australian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Penny%20Wong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20veiled%20allusion%20to%20US%20frustrations%2C%20Blinken%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20really%20comes%20down%20to%2C%20really%2C%20is%20all%20parties%20finding%20ways%20to%20come%20to%20an%20agreement%2C%20not%20look%20for%20reasons%20to%20delay%20or%20to%20say%20no.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20urgent%20that%20all%20parties%20make%20the%20right%20choices%20in%20the%20hours%20and%20days%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFears%20of%20spiraling%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20met%20in%20the%20White%20House's%20heavily%20secured%20Situation%20Room%20with%20his%20national%20security%20team%20including%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20flew%20to%20the%20White%20House%20after%20a%20weekend%20home%20in%20Delaware%2C%20and%20after%20a%20kiss%20for%20First%20Lady%20Jill%20Biden%2C%20he%20headed%20straight%20into%20the%20Oval%20Office%20without%20commenting%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20that%20Biden%20and%20the%20Jordanian%20king%20in%20their%20call%20%26quot%3Bdiscussed%20their%20efforts%20to%20de-escalate%20regional%20tensions%2C%20including%20through%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20hostage%20release%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20Abdullah%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%20and%20permanent%20ceasefire%20to%20end%20the%20catastrophe%20in%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20%26quot%3Bceasing%20all%20escalatory%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20readout%20by%20the%20Jordanian%20royal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20fired%20directly%20at%20Israel%20in%20April%2C%20taking%20their%20long%20shadow%20war%20into%20the%20open%20following%20a%20strike%20on%20an%20Iranian%20diplomatic%20building%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20helped%20intercept%20the%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20and%20damage%20was%20minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jordan%20--%20in%20a%20delicate%20position%20with%20its%20large%20Palestinian%20population%20and%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Israel%20--%20has%20insisted%20it%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20battleground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20said%20that%20in%20April%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20able%20to%20chart%20a%20path%20that%20ultimately%20got%20us%20through%20that%20time%20without%20tipping%20into%20a%20wider%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20every%20time%20you%20have%20one%20of%20these%20cycles%20of%20escalation%2C%20you%20have%20a%20risk%20of%20parties%20miscalculating%2C%20you%20have%20the%20risk%20of%20them%20taking%20actions%20that%20get%20out%20of%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20s