ailable%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20were%20briefed%20on%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20discussed%20the%20steps%20we%20are%20taking%20to%20defend%20our%20forces%20and%20respond%20to%20any%20attack%20against%20our%20personnel%20in%20a%20manner%20and%20place%20of%20our%20choosing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Iraqi%20military%20source%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20multiple%20rockets%20were%20fired%20at%20the%20base%2C%20with%20some%20landing%20inside%20it%20and%20another%20hitting%20a%20nearby%20village%20but%20not%20causing%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20commander%20in%20a%20pro-Iran%20armed%20group%20told%20AFP%20that%20at%20least%20two%20rockets%20targeted%20the%20base%2C%20without%20saying%20who%20had%20carried%20out%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20in%20the%20group%20and%20a%20security%20source%20confirmed%20an%20attack%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20attacks%20were%20frequent%20early%20in%20the%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20Palestinian%20militants%20in%20Gaza%20but%20since%20then%20have%20largely%20halted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20rocket%20fire%20comes%20as%20fears%20grow%20of%20an%20attack%20by%20Iran%20and%20its%20allies%20on%20Israel%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20top%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%20figures%20in%20strikes%20last%20week%20either%20blamed%20on%20or%20claimed%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%20Series%20of%20attacks%20-%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20killings%2C%20with%20both%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20vowing%20retaliation%2C%20are%20among%20the%20most%20serious%20series%20of%20tit-for-tat%20attacks%20that%20have%20heightened%20fears%20of%20a%20regional%20conflagration%20stemming%20from%20the%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran-aligned%20%26quot%3BAxis%20of%20Resistance%26