he%20field%20is%20just%20as%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20valuable%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a391486-55f7-4776-8fce-0100b34f683c%5C%22%3EAI%20has%20made%20computer%20science%20more%2C%20not%20less%2C%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20wave%20is%20actually%20driving%20demand%20for%20computing%20professionals%20in%20general%2C%20because%20maturing%20AI%20is%20transformative%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20integrated%20into%20many%20facets%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comp.nus.edu.sg%2F~kanmy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKan%20Min%20Yen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20computer%20science%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20Kan%20said%2C%20is%20because%20computer%20science%20isn't%20so%20much%20about%20coding%20as%20it%20is%20an%20approach%20to%20solving%20problems.%20He%20added%20that%20AI%20at%20its%20essence%20is%20just%20another%20tool%20that%20software%20engineers%20can%20use%20in%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proper%20development%20and%20use%20of%20AI%20still%20requires%20fundamental%20knowledge%20of%20software%20engineering%2C%20data%20management%2C%20and%20security%2C%20all%20tenets%20of%20a%20holistic%20computing%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20Kan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-computer-science-professor-prisoners-use-phones-cs50-free-class-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Malan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20professor%20at%20Harvard%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20won't%20displace%20software%20engineers%20in%20the%20near%20term%20and%20would%20instead%20amplify%20their%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsider%20just%20how%20many%20more%20features%20they%20can%20implement%2C%20how%20many%20more%20bugs%20they%20can%20fix%2C%20if%20they%20have%20a%20virtual%20assistant%20by%20their%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Malan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20concerns%20over%20AI's%20impact%20on%20tech%20jobs%20might%20also%20be%20overblown%20since%20most%20companies%20aren't%20just%20looking%20for%20code%20monkeys%20to%20churn%20out%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20AI%20enhances%20efficiency%20and%20allows%20people%20to%20do%20more%20with%20less%2C%20writing%20code%20is%20just%20a%20part%20of%20a%20software%20engineer's%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fadriangohjw%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdrian%20Goh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nodeflair.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENodeFlair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20job%20board%20for%20tech%20professionals%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEngineers%20also%20need%20to%20understand%20requirements%20from%20designers%2C%20project%20managers%2C%20and%20business%20teams%2C%20translating%20those%20requirements%20into%20functional%20code%20%E2%80%94%20tasks%20that%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20context%20and%20nuanced%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259336584-3828-484c-a10e-9ed8374cba38%5C%22%3EThe%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20haven't%20changed%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20computer%20science%20graduates%20should%20start%20building%20a%20niche%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20job%20hunt%20by%20studying%20other%20subjects%20like%20finance%20and%20law%2C%20Malan%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20the%20world%20is%20only%20becoming%20more%20technological%20and%20will%20still%20need%20skilled%20and%20educated%20humans%20to%20steer%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOdds%20are%20AI%20will%20impact%20finance%20and%20law%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Malan%20suggested%20that%20students%20embrace%20lifelong%20learning%20while%20not%20neglecting%20the%20tried-and-tested%20approach%20of%20working%20on%20their%20own%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20portfolio%20of%20projects%20under%20one's%20belt%20can%20certainly%20help%2C%20insofar%20as%20you%20can%20draw%20on%20those%20experiences%20in%20applications%20and%20interviews%20to%20paint%20a%20picture%20of%20how%20you%20think%20and%20solve%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20focusing%20on%20the%20technical%20aspects%20of%20the%20job%2C%20Kan%20said%20that%20students%20shouldn't%20forget%20about%20their%20soft%20skills%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoftware%20engineering%20as%20a%20profession%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20really%20a%20team%20sport%20that%20prizes%20communication%2C%20coordination%2C%20and%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComputer%20science%20is%20an%20evergreen%20profession%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20tools%20but%20more%20about%20the%20mindset%20and%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20Kan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20define%20the%20worth%20of%20a%20carpenter%20by%20her%20tools%20or%20a%20chef%20by%20his%20knives%2C%20but%20by%20the%20furniture%20or%20dishes%20they%20create.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20with%20a%20computer%20science-trained%20professional%20using%20tools%20such%20as%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelax-college-kids-ai-will-not-kill-computer-science-degree-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722893762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66abaf20aab37011780c6c82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelax-college-kids-ai-will-not-kill-computer-science-degree-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harvard%20computer%20science%20professor%20David%20Malan%20told%20BI%20that%20far%20from%20displacing%20software%20engineers%2C%20AI%20would%20amplify%20their%20productivity%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%2