n%20Apple%20hardware%20or%20the%20Safari%20and%20Mozilla%20browsers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20lawyers%20argued%20that%20Google%20achieved%20and%20perpetuated%20its%20dominance%20--%20and%20strangled%20rivals%20--%20through%20these%20default%20deals%20that%20also%20expanded%20to%20Samsung%20and%20other%20device%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20concluded%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Google's%20violation%20of%20the%20Sherman%20Act%20did%20not%20have%20%26quot%3Banticompetitive%20effects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722891780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F40cmfqso_google-generic_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-judge-rules-google-broke-antitrust-law-in-search-case-6271587%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alphabet's%20Google%20broke%20the%20law%20to%20cement%20its%20dominance%20over%20online%20searches%20and%20related%20ads%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20ruled%20on%20Monday%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Justice%20Department's%20first%20victory%20against%20a%20monopoly%20in%20more%20than%2020%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-judge-rules-google-broke-antitrust-law-in-search-case-6271587%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-judge-rules-google-broke-antitrust-law-in-search-case-6271587%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-judge-rules-google-broke-antitrust-law-in-search-case-6271587%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jennifer%20Garner%20Shares%20Her%20Intense%20Elektra%20Workout%20Plan%20for%20%E2%80%98Deadpool%20%26amp%3B%20Wolverine%2C%E2%80%99%20Including%20