shington%20Commanders).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20elaborate%20ruse%2C%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1LsNBA2XwXU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOperation%20Flagship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20began%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20fictional%20Flagship%20International%20Sports%20Television%2C%20which%20was%20a%20riff%20on%20the%20acronym%20FIST%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usmarshals.gov%2Fwho-we-are%2Fhistory%2Fhistorical-reading-room%2Ffugitive-investigative-strike-teams-no-such-thing-free-lunch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFugitive%20Investigative%20Strike%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fake%20corporation%20mailed%20invitations%20to%20the%20last%20known%20addresses%20of%20more%20than%203%2C000%20wanted%20people%2C%20telling%20them%20they%20won%20free%20tickets%20to%20a%20Redskins%20vs.%20Cincinnati%20Bengals%20football%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20101%20criminals%20who%20responded%20to%20the%20phony%20invitations%20attended%20a%20brunch%20at%20the%20Washington%20Convention%20Center%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20game%20to%20pick%20up%20their%20complimentary%20tickets%2C%20celebrate%20their%20good%20fortune%2C%20and%20get%20free%20transportation%20to%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20actuality%2C%20the%20fugitives%20were%20surrounded%20by%20over%20100%20undercover%20cops%20posing%20as%20cheerleaders%2C%20mascots%2C%20maintenance%20crew%20members%2C%20and%20other%20venue%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fugitives%20were%20then%20split%20into%20smaller%2C%20more%20manageable%20groups.%20When%20it%20came%20time%20for%20the%20big%20surprise%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20burst%20into%20the%20room%20and%20arrested%20the%20fugitives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fdc-sports-bog%2Fwp%2F2015%2F12%2F18%2Fhow-u-s-marshals-used-redskins-tickets-to-bust-fugitives-in-1985-sting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2