ests%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20was%20raised%20in%20Japan%20at%200%25%20interest%20rates%20and%20used%20to%20speculate%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20so%20I%20think%20that's%20all%20coming%20unglued%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20margin%20calls%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20happen%20pretty%20quick%20and%20the%20unwind%20should%20be%20over%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unwind%20in%20the%20yen%20carry%20trade%20will%20go%20down%20as%20the%20biggest%20ever%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Monday%20note%20from%20Societe%20Generale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocGen's%20chief%20global%20currency%20strategist%20Kit%20Juckes%20said%20that%20while%20he%20is%20treating%20Monday's%20plunge%20in%20stock%20prices%20with%20suspicion%2C%20as%20big%20moves%20on%20Monday%20tend%20to%20%26quot%3Bhappen%20in%20a%20vacuum%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20is%20still%20room%20for%20downside%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%20going%20forward%20for%20markets%20isn't%20what%20the%20Japanese%20yen%20does%2C%20but%20rather%20what%20US%20tech%20stocks%20do%2C%20according%20to%20Juckes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rally%20was%20huge%2C%20the%20valuations%20were%20stretched%20and%20Warren%20Buffett's%20liking%20for%20cash%20is%20making%20headlines%20again.%20If%20that%20market%20keeps%20falling%2C%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20Fed%2C%26quot%3B%20Juckes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuckes%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20labour%20market%20remains%20tight%2C%20the%20economy%20is%20still%20growing.%20That%20would%20change%20if%20equities%20fell%20too%20far%2Ffast%2C%20and%20it%20would%20change%20if%20the%20August%20jobs%20report%20at%20the%20start%20of%20September%20was%20very%20weak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYardeni%20maintained%20his%20positive%20outlook%20on%20stocks%20despite%20the%20sharp%20rise%20in%20market%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20too%20late%20to%20panic%20is%20sort%20of%20my%20attitude%20towards%20this%20sell-off%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20economy%20is%20doing%20better%2C%20and%20I'm%20blaming%20the%20weather%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20weakness%20in%20July's%20employment%20report%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20still%20don't%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20get%20a%20recession%20out%20of%20all%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-yen-carry-trade-unwind-fed-japan-rates-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722887613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b129dab4912df3ae190328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-yen-carry-trade-unwind-fed-japan-rates-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20yen%20carry%20trade%20refers%20to%20investors%20borrowing%20money%20at%20near-zero%20interest%20rates%20in%20Japan%20and%20then%20redeploying%20that%20cash%20into%20higher%20yielding%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A188%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-yen-carry-trade-unwind-fed-japan-rates-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20didn't%20disclose%20yet%20another%20trip%20with%20Harlan%20Crow%2C%20senator%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clarence%20Thomas%20wearing%20his%20robes%20and%20looking%20down%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b12481a5247369a3e9913e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Ron%20Wyden%20lists%2019%20trips%20that%20Thomas%20has%20taken%20on%20Crow's%20private%20jet%20since%202010.%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClarence%20Thomas%20didn't%20disclose%20a%202010%20trip%20on%20billionaire%20Harlan%20Crow's%20jet%2C%20a%20Democratic%20senator%20alleged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20allegations%20are%20part%20of%20a%20Senate%20investigation%20into%20Crow's%20taxes%20and%20financial%20ties%20to%20Thomas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20week%20ago%2C%20Biden%20proposed%20huge%20changes%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20including%20a%20binding%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20missed%20publicly%20disclosing%20another%20jaunt%20on%20billionaire%20and%20conservative%20megadonor%20Harlan%20Crow's%20private%20jet%2C%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Ron%20Wyden%20of%20Oregon%20alleged%20in%20a%20letter%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fchairman_wyden_to_harlan_crow_-_080524pdf.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Thomas%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Virginia%20Thomas%2C%20took%20a%20round-trip%20flight%20on%20Crow's%20private%20jet%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20November%20of%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyden%2C%20who%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Senate%20Finance%20Committee%2C%20sent%20the%20letter%20to%20Crow's%20lawyers%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20right-wing%20donor%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20justice.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20writes%20that%20Customs%20and%20Border%20patrol%20records%20show%20evidence%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20but%20that%20Thomas%20did%20not%20list%20it%20on%20his%202010%20financial%20disclosures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustices%20are%20legally%20obligated%20to%20fill%20out%20financial%20disclosure%20forms%20every%20year%2C%20which%20include%20any%20external%20sources%20of%20income%20and%20gifts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20had%20amended%20some%