expenses%20and%20received%20tax%20deductions%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Thomas%20nor%20Wyden%20immediately%20responded%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20ethics%20have%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20the%20new%20revelations%20come%20just%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-aims-rein-in-supreme-court-saying-its-gone-rogue-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Biden%20proposed%20sweeping%20changes%20at%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20binding%20code%20of%20conduct.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Biden's%20proposals%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-supreme-court-reform-plan-dead-on-arrival-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20to%20get%20Republican%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20spotlight%20on%20an%20increasingly%20unpopular%20high%20court%20and%20on%20Thomas%20in%20particular%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrips-justice-clarence-thomas-took-with-harlan-crow-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20trips%20with%20Crow%3C%2Fa%3E%20sparked%20much%20of%20the%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-disclose-harlan-crow-jet-trip-hawaii-senator-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722887536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b1267ea5247369a3e992f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-disclose-harlan-crow-jet-trip-hawaii-senator-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sen.%20Ron%20Wyden%20alleged%20that%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20failed%20to%20disclose%20another%20trip%20on%20billionaire%20Harlan%20Crow's%20jet%2C%20this%20time%20from%202010.%22%2C%22aut