3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2sdnjgdg_sheikh-hasina_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E'In%20my%20beginning%20is%20my%20end.'%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20situation%20in%20the%20world%20that%20cannot%20be%20explained%20through%20poetry%20in%20general%2C%20T.S.%20Eliot's%20in%20particular.%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20one%20of%20the%20longest-serving%20heads%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20world%2C%20has%20demitted%20office%20after%20a%20month%20of%20bloodshed%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Her%20life%20seems%20to%20be%20coming%20full%20circle-the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20sought%20refuge%20in%20India%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20is%20this.%20Humiliated%20by%20the%20West%20Pakistan%20establishment%20despite%20decisively%20winning%20the%201970%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20-%20Hasina's%20father%20-%20gave%20a%20call%20for%20Independence%20and%20after%20a%20year%20of%20bloodshed%2C%20Bangladesh%20came%20into%20existence.%20Mujib%20was%20killed%3B%20a%20terrible%20beauty%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependence%20Is%20A%20Terrible%20Thing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependence%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20beauty.%20It%20is%20also%20terrible.%20Rarely%20does%20it%20come%20into%20being%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20violence.%20This%20holds%20more%20succinctly%20for%20South%20Asia%20than%20any%20other%20part%20of%20the%20world%2C%20or%20at%20least%20it%20feels%20so%20given%20the%20sheer%20numbers.%20In%20India's%20public%20imagination%2C%201971%20is%20all%20about%20Mukti%20Bahini%20and%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20joining%20hands%20in%20birthing%20Bangladesh.%20It's%20about%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Sam%20Manekshaw.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20Yahya%20Khan%20cancelled%20the%20Pakistan%20National%20Assembly%20on%20March%201%2C%201971%2C%20more%20than%20300%20ethnic%20Biharis%20were%20murdered%20by%20Mujib's%20supporters%20even%20before%20the%20latter's%20call%20for%20mobilisation.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20establishment%20launched%20Operation%20Searchlight%20to%20cull%20Awami%20League%20supporters%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%20This%20was%20touted%20as%20a%20legitimate%20state%20action%20to%20punish%20conspiracy%20and%20unrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quick%20reckoner%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20how%20even%20the%20noblest%20political%20causes%20have%20their%20genesis%20in%20questionable%20actions%20and%20their%20motives.%20They%20often%20have%20a%20legacy%20of%20blood.%20Hasina%20and%20some%20of%20her%20family%20members%20were%20rescued%20in%201975%20by%20Indian%20forces%20after%20Mujib's%20erstwhile%20compatriots%20and%20comrades%20turned%20against%20him.%20Mujib%20was%20murdered%20in%20his%20residence%20on%20August%2015%2C%201975%2C%20along%20with%20six%20members%20of%20his%20immediate%20family%2C%20including%20his%20wife%2C%20brother%20and%20sons.%20It%20was%20the%20same%20old%20story%20of%20Brutus%20stabbing%20Caesar%3B%2032%20Dhanmondi%20was%20the%20new%20Largo%20di%20Torre%20Argentina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20hailed%20as%20a%20messiah%2C%20Mujib%20had%20been%20facing%20criticism%20on%20several%20counts%3A%20corruption%2C%20nepotism%2C%20mismanagement%20of%20the%201974%20famine%2C%20favouritism%2C%20etc.%20He%20was%20accused%20of%20turning%20into%20what%20he%20once%20opposed%20-%20a%20dictator.%20This%20has%20been%20Hasina's%20history%20and%20legacy.%20Fleeing%20Bangladesh%20for%20safety%20once%20again%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20may%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20Was%20Never%20Going%20To%20Be%20Easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20Bangladesh%20has%20witnessed%20election-time%20violence%20between%20the%20ruling%20Awami%20League%20and%20the%20opposition%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party.%20Concerns%20around%20Bangladesh's%20ability%20to%20conduct%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20have%20loomed%20large%20over%20electoral%20processes.%20The%20number%20of%20clashes%20between%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20more%20than%20tripled%20from%20the%202018%20elections.%20Hasina's%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20was%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy%20by%20any%20means.%20As%20predicted%2C%20the%20results%20were%20disputed%20by%20the%20BNP%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties.%20She%20handled%20the%20charges%20like%20any%20astute%20politician.%20The%20student-led%20protests%20over%20quotas%20in%20government%20jobs%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20her%20Achilles's%20heel.%20South%20Asia%2C%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20is%20quite%20forgiving%20of%20politicians%20and%20regimes.%20But%20only%20to%20a%20certain%20extent.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20governments%20are%20seen%20to%20be%20at%20war%20only%20with%20their%20political%20and%20ideological%20opponents%2C%20the%20voters%20may%20not%20care.%20When%20the%20attack%20reaches%20their%20doorsteps%2C%20people%20rise.%20They%20may%20not%20succeed%20in%20overthrowing%20a%20regime%20always%2C%20they%20make%20their%20intent%20felt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20an%20accretion%20of%20a%20historical%20political%20feud%20between%20the%20two%20largest%20parties%2C%20the%20military's%20constant%20hankering%20for%20power%2C%20anti-incumbency%2C%20and%20a%20genuine%20concern%20for%20the%20deteriorating%20participatory%20democracy%20in%20the%20country.%20Adding%20to%20this%20mix%20is%20the%20curious%20case%20of%20secularist%20authoritarianism.%20The%20so-called%20'Bangladesh%20model'%20is%20hailed%20by%20the%20establishment%20in%20India%2C%20a%20secular%20republic%2C%20and%20decried%20by%20Pakistan.%20But%20there%20have%20been%20some%20genuine%20concerns%20about%20how%20Awami%20League%20has%20been%20using%20secularism%20as%20a%20calling%20card%20to%20cull%20all%20forms%20of%20dissent.%20Post-Islamism%2C%20as%20proposed%20by%20Hasina's%20party%2C%20remains%20a%20Holy%20Grail%20project%20for%20Bangladesh%3A%20ever%20elusive%2C%20always%20used%20for%20mass%20mobilisation%2C%20never%20attained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Deja%20Vu%20Moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sheikh%20family%20has%20now%20seen%20and%20experienced%20it%20all%20-%20from%20all%20the%20possible%20vantage%20points.%20They%20have%20been%20both%20the%20oppressed%20and%20the%20oppressor.%20The%20hunter%20and%20the%20hunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20deja%20vu%20moment%20for%20Bangladesh.%20And%20it's%20both%20a%20deja%20vu%20moment%20and%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning%20for%20India.%20Brutal%20and%20bloody%20regime%20changes%20are%20inevitable%20when%20reason%20and%20rapprochement%20fail.%20The%20new%20order%20may%20not%20always%20be%20in%20line%20with%20the%20expectations%3B%20it%20may%20even%20be%20worse.%20But%20the%20desire%20to%20overthrow%20the%20dysfunctional%2C%20perceived%20or%20real%2C%20order%20is%20an%20all-consuming%20passion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20end%20it%20with%20Eliot's%20verse%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E'In%20succession%3Cbr%3E%5CnHouses%20rise%20and%20fall%2C%20crumble%2C%20are%20extended%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAre%20removed%2C%20destroyed%2C%20restored%2C%20or%20in%20their%20place%3Cbr%3E%5CnIs%20an%20open%20field%2C%20or%20a%20factory%2C%20or%20a%20by-pass.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOld%20stone%20to%20new%20building%2C%20old%20timber%20to%20new%20fires%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnOld%20fires%20to%20ashes%2C%20and%20ashes%20to%20the%20earth%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhich%20is%20already%20flesh%2C%20fur%20and%20faeces%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnBone%20of%20man%20and%20beast%2C%20cornstalk%20and%20leaf.'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722870300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq9r7kic8_sheikh-hasina_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsheikh-hasina-and-family-when-the-hunted-is-also-the-hunter-6269970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20one%20of%20the%20longest-serving%20heads%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20world%2C%20has%20demitted%20office%20after%20a%20month%20of%20bloodshed%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Her%20life%20seems%20to%20be%20coming%20full%20circle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsheikh-hasina-and-family-when-the-hunted-is-also-the-hunter-6269970%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Sugarcane%20Fields%20to%20Paris%20Olympics%3A%20Javelin%20Thrower%20Annu%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20Record-Breaking%20Journey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%2031-year-old%20Annu%20Rani%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20javelin%20qualification%20on%207%20August%2C%202024%2C%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20take%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20life%20of%20this%20eight-time%20national%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20village%20of%20Bahadarpur%2C%20Meerut%2C%20Annu%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family%20with%20a%20love%20for%20cricket%2C%20where%20she%20amused%20herself%20by%20throwing%20cricket%20balls.%20Her%20brother%20Upendra%20was%20impressed%20by%20her%20strength%20during%20a%20cricket%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20runner%20myself%20but%20I%20was%20always%20fascinated%20with%20javelin.%20Whenever%20I%20went%20to%20local%20meets%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20the%20event.%20Annu%20used%20to%20play%20cricket%20with%20us%20and%20had%20a%20strong%20arm.%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20try%20javelin%2C%E2%80%9D%20Upendra%20shared%20in%20an%20interview.%20So%20he%20began%20coaching%20Annu%20by%20having%20her%20throw%20sticks%20in%20an%20empty%20sugarcane%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20means%20to%20buy%20a%20javelin%2C%20Annu%20fashioned%20her%20own%20in%202010%20when%20she%20turned%2018.%20Whether%20she%20was%20tossing%20cricket%20balls%20or%20sugarcane%20sticks%2C%20these%20activities%20helped%20her%20build%20strong%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20Amarpal%E2%80%99s%20disapproval%20did%20not%20deter%20Annu%2C%20who%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20marry%20early%20like%20other%20girls%20in%20her%20village.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20forbidden%20from%20wearing%20T-shirts%20and%20playing%20sports.%20Financial%20constraints%20forced%20her%20to%20borrow%20jerseys%20and%20javelins%20from%20other%20players%20and%20make%20do%20with%20their%20oversized%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20I%20come%20from%2C%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20depend%20on%20their%20parents%20and%20must%20always%20beg%20their%20father%20or%20brother%20for%20anything%20they%20need.%20After%20turning%2020%2C%20girls%20are%20often%20considered%20a%20burden%20and%20married%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20expectation%20that%20women%20should%20constantly%20depend%20on%20men%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20marriage%2C%20disturbed%20Annu%20and%20made%20the%20world%20seem%20limited%20for%20women.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20accept%20the%20life%20expected%20of%20her%20and%20viewed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359674%2Flovlina-borgohain-paris-olympics-2024-indian-boxer-assam-first-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20as%20her%20way%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Without%20a%20clear%20path%20or%20training%20options%2C%20she%20chose%20javelin%20because%20it%20required%20just%20a%20sugarcane%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20wanted%20to%20initially%20stick%20to%20local%20customs%20and%20marry%20her%20off.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20youngest%20sibling%2C%20she%20managed%20to%20persuade%20him%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20study%20until%20Class%2012%2C%20with%20support%20from%20her%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20her%20training%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20farm%20fields%2C%20and%20she%20kept%20it%20discreet.%20She%20practised%20with%20sugarcane%20sticks%20after%20school.%20After%20a%20schoolboy%20reported%20her%20activities%20to%20her%20father%2C%20asking%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20your%20daughter%20is%20playing%20in%20the%20fields%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20her%20father%2C%20surprised%2C%20went%20to%20the%20school%20to%20scold%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20teacher%20advised%20him%20to%20let%20Annu%20continue%20for%20a%20while.%20%E2%80%9CShe%E2%80%99ll%20stop%20when%20she%E2%80%99s%20had%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20teacher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20her%20father%20began%20to%20show%20his%20support.%20He%20would%20cycle%2C%20with%20her%20running%20alongside%20him.%20To%20keep%20her%20training%20discreet%2C%20he%20scheduled%20her%20practice%20sessions%20before%20the%20villagers%20returned%20from%20work%20to%20avoid%20drawing%20their%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20chapter%20began%20in%20Annu%E2%80%99s%20life%20after%20she%20clinched%20gold%20at%20the%202014%20National%20Inter-State%20Athletics%20Championship%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20breaking%20a%2014-year-old%20national%20record%20with%20a%2058.83m%20javelin%20throw.%20She%20qualified%20for%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20where%20she%20finished%20eighth.%20Her%20father%2C%20now%20confident%20in%20her%20potential%2C%20encouraged%20her%20to%20continue%20with%20javelin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Annu%20achieved%20a%20personal%20best%20of%2063.82m%20at%20the%20Indian%20Open%20Javelin%20Throws%20Competition%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20national%20record%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20javelin%20throw%20in%20India.%20She%20also%20made%20history%20at%20the%202023%20Asian%20Games%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20win%20gold%20in%20javelin%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2062.92m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20prepares%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%2C%20Annu%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20rise%20from%20throwing%20sugarcane%20sticks%20to%20setting%20national%20records%20and%20winning%20gold%20medals%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259922%2Fneeraj-chopra-javelin-tokyo-olympics-haryana-obesity-world-champion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%20of%20javelin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20story%20of%20unyielding%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Annu%20Rani%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsY2DrGSvMD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40annurani_%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportskeeda.com%2Fsummer-olympics%2Fnews-who-annu-rani-all-need-know-indian-woman-javelin-thrower-competing-paris-2024-olympics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Annu%20Rani%3F%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20Indian%20woman%20javelin%20thrower%20competing%20at%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3A%20by%20Karan%20Sethi%20for%20sportskeeda.com%2C%20Published%20on%205%20August%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%