20his%20idea%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20September%202020%20with%20Rs%2020%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket.%20Having%20already%20quit%20CA%20preparation%20after%20finishing%20the%20Inter%20exams%2C%20his%20family%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20happy.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20runs%20a%20small%20shop%20and%20sent%20me%20to%20Delhi%20for%20schooling.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20study%20well%20and%20find%20a%20good%20job.%20When%20I%20quit%20and%20returned%20home%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20explaining%20that%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20were%20difficult%20as%20he%20remembers%20%E2%80%9Clooking%20at%20the%20fan%E2%80%9D%20and%20surviving%20on%20the%20savings%20he%20had!%20Chandrashekhar%20then%20started%20looking%20for%20government%20schemes%20and%20loans%20that%20he%20could%20apply%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20registering%20%E2%80%98Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20found%20his%20first%20investor%20in%20an%20incubator%20in%20Pune.%20The%20startup%20received%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20August%202021%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20series%20of%20grants%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20the%20website%20and%20application%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20technical%20aspects%2C%20the%20founder%20had%20a%20big%20task%20in%20hand%3A%20getting%20customers%20and%20workers%20to%20sign%20up.%20After%20hiring%20seven%20members%20for%20his%20team%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20wooing%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20for%20blue-collar%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20a%20mobile%20shop%20or%20small%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20signed%20up%20these%20shop%20owners%20as%20business%20associates.%20They%20would%20help%20workers%20register%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-i