ng-senior-citizens-india-running-successful-startups-isro-restaurants-oil-business-daycares%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boxer%20Lovlina%20Borgohain%E2%80%99s%20Historical%20Path%20From%20Working%20in%20Paddy%20Fields%20to%20Reaching%20Paris%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELovlina%20Borgohain%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20boxing%20champion%20from%20Assam%20who%20has%20been%20representing%20India%20at%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20advanced%20to%20the%20quarter-finals%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%2075kg%20category%20after%20defeating%20Norway%E2%80%99s%20Sunniva%20Hofstad%20On%20Wednesday%2C%2031%20July.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovlina%20is%20now%20just%20one%20step%20away%20from%20winning%20a%20second%20Olympic%20medal%20when%20she%20will%20face%20top%20seed%20Li%20Qian%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20China%20in%20the%20quarter-finals%20on%20Sunday%2C%204th%20August.%20Winning%20the%20bout%20will%20guarantee%20her%20a%20bronze%20medal%20which%20will%20mark%20a%20historic%20moment%20for%20her%20in%20Indian%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovlina%20is%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20first%20Olympic%20gold%20medalist%20and%20the%20third%20Indian%20boxer%20to%20bag%20an%20Olympic%20boxing%20medal%20after%20Vijender%20Singh%20in%20Beijing%202008%20and%20Mary%20Kom%20in%20London%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Bara%20Mukhia%20in%20Assam%2C%20Lovlina%E2%80%99s%20boxing%20journey%20began%20after%20seeing%20American%20boxer%20Muhammad%20Ali%20in%20a%20newspaper%20in%20class%205.%20Though%20initially%20trained%20in%20Muay%20Thai%2C%20she%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20boxing%20coach%20Padum%20Boron%2C%20who%20brought%20her%20to%20Guwahati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Lovlina%E2%80%99s%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20win%2C%20Baro%20Mukhia%20lacked%20water%2C%20roads%2C%20and%20electricity.%20Her%20victory%20spurred%20a%20complete%20transformation%20of%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20her%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHer%20parents%20were%20pitied%20for%20not%20having%20sons%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lovlina%E2%80%99s%20father%20earned%20just%20Rs%204%2C000%20a%20month%20and%20supported%20the%20family%20on%20this%20modest%20income.%20While%20local%20attitudes%20initially%20resisted%20women%20in%20boxing%2C%20Lovlina%E2%80%99s%20Olympic%20bronze%20win%20led%20to%20widespread%20celebration%20across%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20shares%20how%20her%20family%2C%20including%20her%20two%20elder%20sisters%2C%20Licha%20and%20Lima%2C%20who%20are%20now%20serving%20the%20nation%20as%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20and%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20has%20been%20her%20pillar%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20how%20in%20the%20village%20they%20would%20often%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259633%2Flovlina-borgohain-tokyo-olympics-medal-india-proud-village-assam%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epity%20my%20parents%20for%20having%20no%20sons%20but%20three%20daughters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%20would%20always%20tell%20us%20to%20do%20something%20to%20prove%20the%20critics%20wrong%2C%20and%20we%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%20%3C%2Fem%3Eafter%20being%20awarded%20an%20Arjuna%20award%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20journey%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovlina%20started%20boxing%20in%202012%20when%20coach%20Padum%20Boron%20invited%20her%20to%20Guwahati.%20She%20initially%20managed%20on%20a%20sparse%20diet%20and%20her%20father%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20to%20support%20her.%20With%20no%20equipment%20available%2C%20she%20used%20empty%20LPG%20cylinders%20for%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20where%20she%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20buy%20a%20flat%20in%20Guwahati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovlina%E2%80%99s%20former%20coach%20Sandhya%20Gurung%20told%20ESPN%20that%20when%20she%20started%20coaching%20Lovlina%2C%20she%20had%20talent%20but%20was%20fearful.%20She%20would%20perform%20well%20against%20weaker%20opponents%20but%20would%20panic%20under%20real%20pressure%2C%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259884%2Flovlina-borgohain-coach-sandhya-gurung-women-boxing-olympic-bronze-medal-tokyo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGurung%20saw%20Lovlina%E2%80%99s%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20pushed%20her%20to%20aim%20for%20the%20next%20Olympics.%20To%20show%20her%20dedication%2C%20Lovlina%20trimmed%20her%20long%20hair%20to%20improve%20her%20performance%20and%20shaved%20it%20all%20off%20in%202018.%20Gurung%20worked%20with%20Lovlina%20to%20sharpen%20her%20jab%2C%20a%20key%20tool%20for%20both%20attacking%20and%20defending.%20She%20also%20taught%20Lovlina%20how%20to%20control%20her%20fear%20during%20close%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELovlina%E2%80%99s%20impressive%20boxing%20career%20also%20includes%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%202023%20Asian%20Games%2C%20along%20with%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%202022%20Asian%20Boxing%20Championships%20and%20the%202023%20IBA%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Boxing%20Championships.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722659400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paris%20Olympics%3A%20Hailing%20from%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Bara%20Mukhia%20in%20Assam%2C%20Lovlina%20Borgohain%E2%80%99s%20boxing%20journey%20began%20when%20she%20was%20in%20Class%205%20and%20came%20across%20a%20picture%20of%20America