0and%20the%20worlds%20of%2031%20other%20people%20diagnosed%20with%20non-speaking%20autism%2C%20who%20have%20bared%20their%20souls%20in%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98Talking%20Fingers%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20Tanya%E2%80%99s%20view%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F60615%2Fautism-sai-connections-empowered-mothers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautism%20is%20not%20something%20to%20be%20wished%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20an%20integral%20piece%20of%20the%20jigsaw%20which%20is%20their%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20perspective%20amazes%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20piece%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20spectrum%20of%20non-speaking%20autism%2C%C2%A0referring%20to%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20person%20with%20autism%20has%20a%20delay%20or%20difficulty%20with%20speech.%20As%20statistics%20in%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%20%3C%2Fem%3Esuggest%2C%20around%2025%20to%2030%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20ASD%20(Autism%20Spectrum%20Disorder)%20are%20minimally%20verbal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20could%20convey%20the%20essence%20of%20non-speaking%20autism%20to%20you%20through%20research%20findings%2C%20news%20publishings%20and%20heavy%20jargon.%20But%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20justice.%20Instead%2C%20a%20sentence%20I%20read%20in%20an%20article%20published%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Autism%20Research%20does%20the%20trick%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EImagine%20you%20answer%20everyone%20who%20says%20something%20to%20you%2C%20but%20only%20you%20can%20hear%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20Philip%20Reyes%2C%20an%20individual%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-speaking%20autism%3C%2Fa%