0we%20stop%20believing%20in%20ourselves.%20It%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20life%20we%20have%20but%20it%20is%20very%20rich.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20Fingers%20is%20an%20ode%20to%2032%20people%20who%20are%20unable%20to%20converse%20in%20the%20way%20we%20think%20as%20%E2%80%98usual%E2%80%99.%20But%20their%20words%20hold%20great%20power.%20And%20so%20do%20their%20dreams.%20As%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Mithul%20Sandeep%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20dream%20job%20is%20to%20join%20ISRO.%20I%20want%20the%20world%20to%20say%20only%20Mithul%20can%20do%20this.%20They%20call%20me%20a%20special%20child.%20I%20will%20show%20them%20that%20I%20am%20special.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBuy%20Talking%20Fingers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F4faebgR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBuy%20Talking%20Fingers%20Volume%202%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F4cd2jrP%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearchautism.org%2Fblog%2Fi-have-nonverbal-autism-heres-what-i-want-you-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20Have%20Nonverbal%20Autism.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20I%20Want%20You%20to%20Know%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Philip%20and%20Lisa%20Reyes%2C%20Published%20on%203%20January%202018.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722496435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-02-at-3.12.37-PM-1721808685.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Compiled%20by%20Padma%20Jyothi%20and%20Chitra%20Paul%2C%20'Talking%20Fingers'%20is%20a%20book%20written%20by%2032%20individuals%20with%20nonspeaking%20autism.%20The%20authors%20use%20this%20book%20to%20share%20their%20dreams%20and%20hopes%2C%20with%20just%20one%20request%20from%20the%20reader--%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20underestimate%20our%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358168%2Fpeople-with-nonspeaking-autism-in-india-talking-fingers-book-authors-padma-jyothi-chitra-paul%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20110%20km%20Long%20River%20Was%20Left%20To%20Die%2C%20Until%20an%20IAS%20Officer%20Helped%20Revive%20It%20in%206%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoughly%2050%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tributary%20of%20the%20mighty%20Ganges%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20lifeline%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20Sambhal%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20farmers%20depending%20on%20its%20water%20for%20irrigating%20their%20lush%20green%20paddy%20and%20peppermint%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20river%20that%20passes%20through%2071%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20five%20development%20blocks%20disappeared%20from%20the%20district%20due%20to%20large-scale%20encroachment%20and%20neglect.%20In%202022%2C%20when%20the%20newly-appointed%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20that%20the%20river%20was%20practically%20non-existent.%20We%20could%20only%20see%20small%20%3Cem%3Epuliya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(culverts)%20that%20were%20once%20made%20over%20the%20river.%20At%20several%20points%2C%20farmers%20had%20started%20growing%20crops%20considering%20it%20to%20be%20vacant%20land.%20The%20streak%20of%20the%20river%20was%20not%20completely%20connected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20some%20places%2C%20the%20area%20was%20covered%20in%20small%20puddles.%20The%20river%20was%20encroached%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20lost%20its%20path%20of%20natural%20flow%20downstream.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20nearby%20areas%20would%20remain%20waterlogged%20during%20monsoon.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20acted%20as%20a%20natural%20drainage%20system%20for%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20had%20drastically%20reduced%20in%20the%20area%20as%20farmers%20became%20dependent%20on%20borewells%2C%20which%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20water%20problem%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20hand%20pumps%2C%20as%20deep%20as%2050%20feet%2C%20started%20becoming%20non-functional%20because%20of%20the%20receding%20water%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20former%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359110%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20former%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357468%2Fias-officer-revive-water-table-cdo-varanasi-himanshu-nagpal-rainwater-harvesting-river-rejuvenation-groundwater-recharge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20IAS%20officer%20decided%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20river%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20masterplan%20behind%20the%20river%20rejuvenation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpearheaded%20by%20Manish%2C%20the%20Sambhal%20district%20conducted%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20length%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20Sot%20river%2C%20which%20appeared%20to%20be%20non-existent%2C%20was%20actually%20a%20110%20km%20long%20stretch%20starting%20from%20the%20Amroha%20district%20in%20the%20North%20and%20flowing%20towards%20Budaun%20in%20the%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20administration%20conducted%20a%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20natural%20alignment%20of%20the%20river.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20physical%20demarcation%20of%20the%20region%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20third%20step%20was%20to%20clear%20the%20illegal%20encroachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20was%20to%20remove%20the%20encroachments%20along%20the%20river.%20Using%20the%20revenue%20land%20records%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20there%20were%20huge%20encroachments%20on%20the%20river%20area%20which%20had%20become%20flat%20at%20some%20points.%20Although%20there%20was%20no%20permanent%20construction%2C%20people%20started%20using%20it%20to%20grow%20crops.%20As%20it%20was%20illegal%20usage%2C%20we%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20the%20revenue%20land%20records%20team%20to%20clear%20encroachments%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20step%20was%20desilting%20of%20the%20river%20to%20remove%20fine%20silt%20and%20sediment%20collected%20in%20the%20river%20and%20restore%20it%20to%20its%20natural%20capacity.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20roped%20in%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20workers%20to%20clean%20and%20dig%20the%20riverbed%20afresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20December%202022%2C%20the%20project%20was%20completed%20in%20six%20months%20by%20June%202023.%20During%20the%20last%20monsoon%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348157%2Fmanganga-river-solapur-rejuvenation-efforts-vaijinath-ghongade-awarded-book-parikrama-mangangechi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20river%20captured%20the%20rainwater%20and%20was%20revived%20to%20its%20old%20glory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20region%20was%20also%20free%20from%20waterlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20district%20administration%20roped%20in%20MGNREGA%20workers%20to%20clean%20and%20dig%20the%20riverbed%20afresh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513-300x157.jpg%2