he%20pandemic%20was%20a%20harrowing%20time%20for%20many%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20loved%20ones.%20Usha%20Gupta%20(88)%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20same%20fate%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20Raj%20Kumar.%20But%20even%20as%20she%20fought%20through%20her%20grief%2C%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20underprivileged%20did%20not%20escape%20her.%20Through%20Pickled%20With%20Love%2C%20Gupta%20knew%20she%20could%20tide%20through%20her%20grief%20by%20doing%20what%20she%20loved%20best%20%E2%80%94%20cooking%2C%20while%20also%20reaching%20out%20to%20those%20who%20needed%20funds%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20Instagram%20page%20(%40pickled.withlove)%2C%20proceeds%20from%20the%20business%20helped%20more%20than%2065%2C000%20homeless%20people%20across%20four%20cities%20to%20get%20their%20meals%20amid%20the%20pandemic.%20Gupta%20was%20supported%20by%20her%20granddaughter%20Dr%20Radhika%20Batra%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20paediatrician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%20the%20duo%20created%20a%20brand%20that%20prides%20itself%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F252360%2Fpickles-ponnu-mami-palakkad-mango-lime-customers-chennai-achaar-sale-home-senior-citizen-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epickles%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(savoury%20condiments).%20Their%20main%20ingredient%3F%20Love.%20Though%20having%20started%20with%20three%20flavours%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ekhatta%20aam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sour%20mango)%2C%20grated%20mango%20%3Cem%3Echutney%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Egulabi%20meetha%20achaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sweet%20pickle)%2C%20they%20have%20introduced%20a%20bounty%20of%20other%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGet%20in%20touch%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpickled.withlove%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C